CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 13, 1957, page B6, reads: "For Public Service - Among the cashiers who will serve the public are (left to right) Velma Bohinets, Frances Kujava, Ardelle Douglas, Sheila Cajaldo and Helen Smith."
TitMainTitle: Five cashiers, left to right: Velma Bohinets, Frances Kujava, Ardelle Douglas, Sheila Cajaldo, and Helen Smith. posing at checkout point of large supermarket with sign "Thursday April 11th"
